		<div class="font-polysans  text-black dark:text-gray-ef leading-130">
			<div class="inline pr-4 text-16 font-bold md:text-17">Apple’s first Indian retail store is a
				real looker.
			</div>
			<p class="duet--article--dangerously-set-cms-markup inline font-fkroman text-gray-33 dark:text-gray-ef [&amp;_a]:relative [&amp;_a]:z-10  [&amp;_a]:shadow-underline-blurple dark:[&amp;_a]:shadow-underline-franklin [&amp;_a:hover]:text-blurple [&amp;_a:hover]:shadow-underline-blurple dark:[&amp;_a:hover]:text-franklin dark:[&amp;_a:hover]:shadow-underline-franklin">
				A new Apple Store is <a
					href="https://www.apple.com/newsroom/2023/04/apple-bkc-in-mumbai-opens-for-customers-this-tuesday/">opening
				in Mumbai tomorrow</a>, marking the iPhone manufacturer’s <a
					href="/2023/4/6/23673372/apple-india-retail-store-mumbai-bkc">first retail location
				in the country</a>. It’ll be joined by a <a
					href="https://www.apple.com/newsroom/2023/04/apple-bkc-opens-april-18-and-apple-saket-opens-april-20/">second
				store in Delhi opening on April 20th</a>. </p>
			<p class="duet--article--dangerously-set-cms-markup mt-12 inline-block font-fkroman text-gray-33 dark:text-gray-ef [&amp;_a]:relative [&amp;_a]:z-10  [&amp;_a]:shadow-underline-blurple dark:[&amp;_a]:shadow-underline-franklin [&amp;_a:hover]:text-blurple [&amp;_a:hover]:shadow-underline-blurple dark:[&amp;_a:hover]:text-franklin dark:[&amp;_a:hover]:shadow-underline-franklin">
				But look, I mainly just love the design of this building, which features this cool
				triangular tiled ceiling made out of timber. Check out <a
					href="https://www.apple.com/newsroom/2023/04/apple-bkc-in-mumbai-opens-for-customers-this-tuesday/">Apple’s
				press release</a> for more images.</p><br></div>
